{"tid":1970677,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森 討論區 (161)","createTime":"2020-04-13T10:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T11:19:04.000Z","uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c93554afdb00d07f183eea636586d0949007ecf","tid":1970677,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1001開post時希望可以copy埋置頂</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">(用右上三點可以此內容開新post, 可以的話copy埋 置頂嗰堆)</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Fe5omi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Fe5omi.gif&h=a5d92fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Fe5omi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Fe5omi.gif&h=a5d92fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Fe5omi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Fe5omi.gif&h=a5d92fe7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">置頂</span></strong>有實用資訊</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7pVWSxh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7pVWSxh.jpg&h=b9c4f6eb&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">參觀人哋個島必讀 &mdash;&mdash; 良好島民約章</span></strong><br />\n1. 未經同意唔好走去搖人哋棵樹／執人啲野<br />\n2. 跑步注意安全，唔好踩爛人哋啲花<br />\n3. 個袋滿左之後，唔好周地dump垃圾<br />\n4. 唔好偷人啲野，「摸」完野記得要還<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">買game前你可能會想知 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：隻game玩乜？<br />\nA：比較休閒嘅第二人生。隻game時間係跟現實時間，亦慶祝現實節日例如聖誕，復活節等等。遊戲著重你同動物森民嘅交流互動(隻隻都有自己性格)，慢慢一齊生活 了解對方 成為密友， 同埋裝飾你間屋＆島。今隻主題係無人荒島，亦新增合成元素，你要由零開始<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">還債</span></span></del>建設你心目中嘅理想小島。遊戲節奏比較輕鬆，預你日日開來玩一陣，啱玩嘅可以玩幾年都得。<br />\n<br />\nQ：咩版先有中文？唔同版本可唔可以連機？<br />\nA：乜版都有中文 。可以<br />\n<br />\nQ：Online 玩咩？<br />\nA：你可以去朋友／網友嘅島度一齊開party，一齊hea，一齊砌野，一齊炒<del><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">股票</span></span></del>蘿蔔。<br />\n<br />\nQ：單機會唔會無咁好玩？<br />\nA：唔會，隻game係單機game，主要都係著重起你同動物之間嘅交流互動同埋打理你座島。不過多人連機時一樣有野玩咁解。<br />\n<br />\nQ：對手掣好靚，有無得單買？<br />\nA：暫時只見日本My Nintendo Store有得買，但係<del>唔收香港卡</del>同唔寄香港。 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">更新: 原來已更新可以用PayPal俾錢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ：可唔可以用返以前啲Amiibo ＆ Amiibo Card？<br />\nA：可以。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFFWQrY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFFWQrY.png&h=8c46d7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">圖片來源 YouTube -&gt; rEB1vlAiVxE</code></pre><br />\n<br />\nQ：買game實體定下載版好？有無黃店推介？<br />\nA：隻game預你日日開來玩一陣 實係下載版好，仲唔怕會益代理，真係怕唔啱玩要買實體我會建議你幫襯黃店買水貨。Read: 黃藍黑Game舖大集合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：同一部機唔同user save係共通？<br />\nA：無錯，一部機全部user都係住同一個島。<br />\n<br />\nQ：一機多人玩係點？<br />\nA：只有1P可以推展遊戲進度，2P只係執下素材咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無Cloud Save？咁我壞機點算？<br />\nA：無。但官方講法係「Online會員專用壞機／唔見機時尋回save file功能開發中」 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好反智</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：係咪無得轉移個save去第二部機部度？<br />\nA：暫時無。官方講法係「動森專用 機對機save轉移功能開發中」<br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩動物村民？<br />\nA：今集總共有383個<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好似係</span></span>。全村民「圖鑑」未有，但根據歷作會有鱷魚／食蟻獸／熊／鳥／牛／貓／雞／鹿／狗／鴨／鷹／象／蛙／羊／倉鼠／河馬／猩猩／狼／虎／松鼠／犀牛／兔／豬／企鵝／八爪魚／鴕鳥／鼠／馬騮／獅子／袋鼠／樹熊／馬... 歷代全角色(好多頁): <a href=\"https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanimalcrossing.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FCategory%3ACharacters&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=5f37ae56\" target=\"_blank\">https://animalcrossing.fandom.com/wiki/Category:Characters</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">港版特別主機(電力加強版)</span></strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>※並非數量限定商品。日後將預定再次生產</strong></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">-(<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Ftopics%2Farticle%2Fa_200131_02.html&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=caf7e5b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html</a>)</span><br />\n預訂店鋪一覽: (官方頭盔: ※預訂及商品在庫狀況因店舖實際情況而異，詳情請向各店店員查詢)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fhardware%2Fswitch%2Fstore%2Fanimal.html&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=0b0e4cad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入手請幫襯UNY/APITA/AEON/豐澤</span></strong> (唔經代理拎貨)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/animal_crossing_new_horizons/set/img/img-main-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fanimal_crossing_new_horizons%2Fset%2Fimg%2Fimg-main-06.jpg&h=56e37b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n召集所有3DS版熟悉的面孔同新人一齊加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d40f6da2fef89b9c09ff49979b41c9226e146a","tid":1970677,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"遊戲初期常見問題 // 實用online tools // <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n＞Android/iOS 「Nintendo Switch Online」app可以scan設計QR code，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">連機時可以快速打字傾計</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">遊戲初期常見問題Q&amp;A</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>(太長click入去睇-&gt;) </strong></span><a href=\"https://pastebin.com/kZjMuNXh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FkZjMuNXh&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=9e911d60\" target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/kZjMuNXh</a><br />\n<br />\n股價計算<br />\n<a href=\"https://mikebryant.github.io/ac-nh-turnip-prices/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmikebryant.github.io%2Fac-nh-turnip-prices%2Findex.html&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=a1c14c28\" target=\"_blank\">https://mikebryant.github.io/ac-nh-turnip-prices/index.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">可以開房俾巴絲排隊, 唔駛搞到成個post都係code</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://turnip.exchange/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fturnip.exchange%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=d48fd3b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://turnip.exchange/</a><br />\n外島攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://wuffs.org/acnh/mysterytour.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwuffs.org%2Facnh%2Fmysterytour.html&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=24fb8e17\" target=\"_blank\">https://wuffs.org/acnh/mysterytour.html</a><br />\n設計任意pattern, 可生成qr code scan落遊戲度, 可以匯入任意圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://acpatterns.com/editor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facpatterns.com%2Feditor&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=1b490955\" target=\"_blank\">https://acpatterns.com/editor</a><br />\n分割圖片做幾個正方形，搭上面一齊用效果更佳<br />\n<a href=\"https://pinetools.com/split-image\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpinetools.com%2Fsplit-image&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=4b17e6be\" target=\"_blank\">https://pinetools.com/split-image</a><br />\n設計主題曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://tunes.nooknet.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftunes.nooknet.net%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=1633f472\" target=\"_blank\">https://tunes.nooknet.net/</a><br />\n設計無人島<br />\n<a href=\"https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplanimalcrossing.com%2Fnh%2Fstart%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=e6ee9d29\" target=\"_blank\">https://planimalcrossing.com/nh/start/</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：風水？<br />\nA：主人房擺唔同顏色家具增加運氣，綠 整體，紅 物品，黃 金錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/FRbfJgYp/fengshui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FFRbfJgYp%2Ffengshui.jpg&h=dc333a39&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thonky.com/animal-crossing-new-leaf/feng-shui-guide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thonky.com%2Fanimal-crossing-new-leaf%2Ffeng-shui-guide&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=ca176f23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thonky.com/animal-crossing-new-leaf/feng-shui-guide</a><br />\n<br />\nＱ：花係咪可以配種？<br />\nＡ：同類花種埋一齊，淋水，側邊有機會出新色花<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GL7F8T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GL7F8T.png&h=a012237e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nＱ：點拎多啲礦石？<br />\nＡ：好似幅圖咁整三個窿先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvjEZrt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrvjEZrt.jpg&h=79ad3315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nＱ：巴絲分享，外島捉狼蛛攻略<br />\nＡ：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1942461/page/3?post=67\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1942461/page/3?post=67</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：點解跟哂方法整狼蛛島都係失敗/咁少/咁慢<br />\nA：4月開始蟲類會多左田鱉 田鱉會係河到生 但佢又計係蟲類 所以大大打擊左狼蛛刷新既機率 (解決方法係去冇河既外島)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d392fc1283c1e151d639cc61db7483e81f95f03","tid":1970677,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"點解會隔多左行架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94cb0eff1cc28b7377320d8c191d73c37306483","tid":1970677,"uid":34107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"823586673fe39579207b8f4112500877f8782ca4","tid":1970677,"uid":16039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"巴打真係好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5116bb83f1a3aefe6fdf27144d36cd0c152dd8de","tid":1970677,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f94cb0eff1cc28b7377320d8c191d73c37306483","tid":1970677,"uid":34107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:21:18.000Z","msg":"我開衰左 用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1970671/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1970671/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fdf9be5d7d77bf5c1512f80d8a832de65e0d8968","tid":1970677,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"唔知點解香港獨立d qr code scan 唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a15f3a96d8eeb66bada75a20482fc68a6075824","tid":1970677,"uid":137308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"諗唔到個島叫咩名好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid